  "summary": "Moderate: iperf3 security update",
  "details": "Iperf is a tool which can measure maximum TCP bandwidth and tune various parameters and UDP characteristics. Iperf reports bandwidth, delay jitter, and data-gram loss.  \n\nSecurity Fix(es):  \n\n  * iperf3: iperf Heap Buffer Overflow (CVE-2025-54349)\n\n\nFor more details about the security issue(s), including the impact, a CVSS score, acknowledgments, and other related information, refer to the CVE page(s) listed in the References section.\n",
